messages.messageBody:
How do you get it up there? And what percent of protection does it offer?
Kim

You would put it in before, so that it can have time to change the
pH of the whole vaginal area, although you could put some in after
as well for extra protection.

Judie

Well, I don't think there's ever been a study done which could
calculate the percentage of protection (snicker...) but I'm guessing

high as foam, but slightly less than the pill. Nothing's for sure.
